\mt1 Mak  
\mt2 N…ôgkiarien Huv…ô yame Mak r…®m…®rai  
\imt1 N…ôgkiarien kwakw…ô ye n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e Mak  
\ip \bd ?Pa r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e? \bd* Keinein m…ô pa nhag…®n r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e- n…ômehu…ô kupan kape nim…ôhuak k…®mnhani m…ô Jon Mak r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e. In, p…ôh nien m…ô yermam…ô twelef k…®rik kape Yesu Kristo. M…ôr…®g kamni k…®m…ô in fren huv…ô k…®rik kape Pita yame iriu k…®rav…ôn ik…®n m…®n…ô fam. Ol Wok ramni m…ô in apa kup…ôn, Mak r…®mnor wok iriu Pol, k…®ni ai, m…®v…ôn mor wok iriu Banabas.  
\ip \bd ?R…®m…®rai ramv…ôn k…®mi pa?\bd* Kamni k…®m…ô Mak r…®mnamar…ô apa Rom ye n…®p…®g r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e. K…®ni tukm…ô ror in r…®mnamar…ô iriu Pita, kwas…®g ik…®n k…®shopni Pita. Mak r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e r…®v…ôn k…®mi n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô apa Rom m…®ne yam…ô m…®ne p…ôh nien m…ô kw…ôn…ôr…ôus kap…ô n…ôm…ô Isrel. K…®taw…ô kharkun m…ô ramv…ôn k…®mi n…ôm…ô p…ôh nien m…ô n…ôm…ô Isrel meinai Mak ramhoprai n…®prai norien m…®n…ô kape n…ôm…ô Isrel, k…®ni m…®rai n…ôgkiarien t…®ks…®n ye n…ôgkiarien e kamni k…®m…ô Arameak, yame n…ôm…ô Isrel kw…ônharkun ta. M…ôr…®g Mak rukreik…®n n…ôgkiarien m…®n…ô a r…®v…ôn ye n…ôgkiarien kape n…ôm…ô Gris, yame n…ôm…ô Rom k…®mnhani.  
\ip \bd ?Nar…ôyen r…®mnhawor p…ôn iran m…®ne ye n…®p…®g r…®m…®rai?\bd* Ye n…®p…®g Mak r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e, n…ôm…ô Rom k…®m…®sarmaru ye tan…ô ehu…ô yame rarkurao ye tahik e kamni k…®m…ô Mediterenian. Kap…ôri…ô n…ôgkiarien k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô, k…®ni kasar…ô ye n…ôm…ôrinuyen. Ror p…ôn, r…®mar …ôm…ô tuk n…®ni-…ôrhavyen n…ôgkiarien k…®rik r…®t…ôrhav m…®v…ôn ik…®n m…®n…ô fam. Ye n…®p…®g a, N…ôvsaoyen Huv…ô kape Yesu Kristo r…®mnaiyu aihuaa …ôm…ô ye tan…ô p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n…ô ye swatuk m…®n…ô apa Rom.  
\ip \bd ?R…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e tuk naha?\bd* Mak rorkeikei m…ô tukr…®ni-…ôrhav atuatuk n…ôvsaoyen fam kape Yesu, m…ô in pa, k…®ni r…®mnor naha, k…®ni mamhajoun naha. Tukm…ô ror in rorkeikei m…ô tukr…®v…ôhsi-hakt…ô n…ôr…®gien kape n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô apa Rom, meinai narmam…ô khapsaah k…®m…®sor ahas p…ôn k…®mi …ôri…ô. Mak r…®mn…ôvsao p…®k k…®n n…®p…®g …ôut…ôn yam…ô m…®ne tukr…®piu…ô tuk narmam…ô kape Yesu. K…®ni m…®ni-…ôrhav norien kape Yesu m…ô In m…®n r…®mnamar…ô ye n…®p…®g …ôut…ôn m…®n…ô.  
\c 1  
\s1 Jon Baptaes ram…ôm…®r ye t…®p…ôvs…®k mamni…ôrhav n…ôgkiarien  
\r (Mat 3:1-12; Luk 3:1-18; Jon 1:19-28)  
\p
\v 1 In e N…ôgkiarien Huv…ô kape Yesu Kristo, Ji Kughen.  
\v 2 Profet kup…ôn k…®rik kape Kughen, nhag…®n e Aesea, r…®mn…ôvsao k…®n m…®ni-…ôrhav m…ô, ‚ÄúKughen r…®m…ô,  
\q1 ‚Äú‚ÄòYakamher-pre k…®n yermam…ô k…®rik tuk n…ôvsaoyen k…®n kafak n…ôgkiarien.  
\q2 In tukror apn…ôpen…ô ye swatuk kafam.‚Äô\f + \fr 1:2 \ft Kughen ram…ôgkiar k…®mi Yesu ye ves e.\f*\rq (Mal 3:1)\rq*   
\q1
\v 3 ‚ÄòYermam…ô k…®rik ramok-rapomh ye t…®p…ôvs…®k, mamni m…ô,  
\q2 ‚ÄúTaksor apn…ôpen…ô ye swatuk kape Kughen, yame in Yermaru kap…ôtaw…ô.‚Äù ‚Äô‚Äù\rq (Aes 40:3)\rq*   
\p
\v 4 K…®ni ai kw…ôn k…®rik, nhag…®n e Jon, r…®mau…ô ye t…®p…ôvs…®k, k…®ni mor baptaes ye narmam…ô m…ô tukror n…®mt…ôtien m…ô kw…ôsarar ye n…ôr…®gien kap…ôri…ô tuk t…ôvhag…ô has, k…®ni m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTaksarar ye n…ôr…®gien kap…ômi…ô, m…®sarakik…®n t…ôvhag…ô hah, k…®ni m…®sor baptaes.‚Äù\x - \xo 1:4 \xt Wok 13:24; 19:4 \x*  
\v 5 K…®ni ai narmam…ô fam ye yerkwanu a Judia m…®ne Jerusalem khav…ôn m…®s…ôm in. Mamhani-…ôrhav-p…ôn t…ôvhag…ô has kap…ôri…ô. K…®ni Jon ror baptaes ir…ôri…ô ye nu apa Jodan.  
\v 6 Jon r…®p…ôh n…®v…ôhsi-p…ônien neip…ôn huv…ô k…®rik. Kafan kot k…®mnor k…®n t…®ki narm…®ragh k…®rik, kamni k…®m…ô kamel. K…®ni kafan k…ôt…ôut k…®mnor k…®n t…®ki kau.\f + \fr 1:6 \ft  Neip…ôn a r…ômhen k…®n kape profet kup…ôn k…®rik, nhag…®n e Elaeja.\f* K…®ni nan n…ôv…®g…®nien k…ôvraiyuk …ôm…ô m…®ne sukapak.\x - \xo 1:6 \xt 2 King 1:8; Mat 11:8 \x*  
\v 7 K…®ni in ramni-…ôrhav p…ôn tuk narmam…ô m…ô, ‚ÄúKwas…®g irak, yermam…ô k…®rik e tukru…ô In yerp…®r…®g rapita yo. Yo yakp…ôh n…ômhenien m…ô to yak…ôn…®mkur k…®ni m…®r…®s…®n-ta n…ôr…ôus ye kafan sandel.\x - \xo 1:7 \xt Wok 13:25 \x*  
\v 8 M…ôr…®g yo y…®mnor …ôm…ô baptaes ir…ômi…ô k…®n nu; k…®ni m…ôr…®g In tukror baptaes ir…ômi…ô k…®n Nanm…®n Rhak…ô.‚Äù   
\s1 Jon r…®mnor baptaes ye Yesu  
\r (Mat 3:13-17; Luk 3:21-22)  
\p
\v 9 Ye n…®p…®g a, Yesu r…®mas…®-p…ôn Nasaret, yerkwanu k…®rik ye Galili. Mu…ô e Jon ram…ôm…®r ik…®n. K…®ni ai Jon r…®mnor baptaes iran ye nu apa Jodan.\fig Jon Baptaes r…®mnor baptaes ye Yesu|alt="John the Baptist baptized Jesus" src="CNT5171.jpg" size="span" loc="Top of page" copy="David C. Cook" ref="MRK 1:9" \fig*  
\v 10 N…®p…®g Yesu r…®mneiwaiyu mhek…®mter m…®n ye tame nu, In m…ôm m…ôknek…®n m…ô napu…ô r…®mn…ôkwag. In r…ôm Nanm…®n kape Kughen r…®s…®-p…ôn aik…®n meiwaiyu-p…ô tukun r…ômhen k…®n mak ye tan…ô.  
\v 11 K…®ni ai, n…ôgkiarien k…®rik r…®mas…®-p…ôn ye rao ye neai mamni m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúIk Nar…®k yame yakorkeikei. R…®kik ragien p…®k tuk Ik.‚Äù\x - \xo 1:11 \xt Sam 2:7; Aes 42:1; Mat 12:18; Mak 9:7 \x*   
\s1 Setan r…®mnarkut tuk Yesu  
\r (Mat 4:1-11; Luk 4:1-13)  
\p
\v 12 M…ôknek…®n, Nanm…®n kape Kughen r…®mn…ôkeikei k…®mi Yesu k…®ni m…®k…®r m…®v…ôn apa ye t…®p…ôvs…®k.  
\v 13 Aik…®n, Setan ramarkut m…ô tukrukrao ye n…ôr…®gien kafan kape n…®p…®g foti. Yesu ramar…ô iri…ô nar m…®ragh aparu m…®n…ô. K…®ni m…ôr…®g agelo m…®n…ô k…®m…®sarha huv…ô tukun.\x - \xo 1:13 \xt Sam 91:11-13 \x*   
\s1 Yesu r…®m…®rikakun kafan wok apa Galili  
\r (Mat 4:12-17; Luk 4:14-15)  
\p
\v 14 K…®ni k…®r…ôhsi-p…ôn Jon ye kalabus. Kwas…®g ik…®n, Yesu r…®piv…ôn Galili, mamni-…ôrhav N…ôgkiarien Huv…ô kape Kughen.\x - \xo 1:14 \xt Mak 6:17 \x*  
\v 15 M…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTakt…ôkun ai, r…®nor atuatuk n…®p…®g. Narmaruyen kape Kughen ruau…ô-ta. Taksarar ye n…ôr…®gien kap…ômi…ô tuk t…ôvhag…ô hah kap…ômi…ô, mhani n…ôfrak…®sien ye N…ôgkiarien Huv…ô kape Kughen.‚Äù\x - \xo 1:15 \xt Mat 3:2 \x*   
\s1 Yesu r…®mnokr…ôn k…®n narmam…ô kuas- narmam…ô kape n…®viyen k…ômam  
\r (Mat 4:18-22 Luk 5:1-11)  
\p
\v 16 K…®ni ai, Yesu r…®mn…ôriw…ôk ye n…®kar lugun Galili, k…®ni m…ôm kw…ôr…ô mir k…®raru, nhagriu e Saemon m…®ne naorahini Andru. Iriu kwaruk…®n net, meinai iriu yermam…ô kape n…®viyen k…ômam.  
\v 17 K…®ni Yesu r…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôriu m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúRau…ô m…®rakwas…®g k…®n Yo. P…ôh yakor …ômiru yermam…ô mir kape n…®viyen narmam…ô.‚Äù  
\v 18 M…ôknek…®n kr…ôp…ôh kap…ôriu net, mwarar, m…®rakwas…®g k…®n.   
\p
\v 19 K…®ni Yesu r…ôriw…ôk m…®v…ôn k…ôsk…ôh …ôm…ô m…®n, k…®ni m…ôm kw…ôr…ô mir k…®raru. Kwajikov…ô mir kape Sebedi. Nhagriu e Jemes m…®ne Jon. Kaokw…ôt…ô ye n…ôkwai bot kap…ôriu, k…®ni marajir …ôs…®g…®n net kap…ôriu.  
\v 20 M…ôknek…®n Yesu rokr…ôn k…®n …ôriu. K…®ni ai iriu kw…ôrer mw…ôp…ôh r…®mriu Sebedi ram…ôm…®r ye n…ôkwai bot iri…ô kafan narmam…ô m…®n…ô. K…®ni iriu m…®rakwas…®g k…®n Yesu.   
\s1 Yesu r…®mn…ôko ta yarmh…ô ye yermam…ô k…®rik  
\r (Luk 4:31-37)  
\p
\v 21 Yesu m…®ne narmam…ô kafan k…®mnhav…ôn apa yerkwanu k…®rik, nhag…®n e Kapaneam. K…®ni ye Sabat m…®n k…®rik, Yesu r…®v…ôn apa nim…ôhuak kape n…ôm…ô Isrel, k…®ni mamhajoun narmam…ô.  
\v 22 Narmam…ô k…®m…®s…ôr…®g kafan n…ôgkiarien, k…®sakur, meinai kafan n…ôgkiarien nanm…®n aik…®n, r…®p…ôh n…ômhenien k…®n n…ôgkiarien kape n…ômhajoun kape Loa kape Moses.\x - \xo 1:22 \xt Mat 7:28-29 \x* \fig Kapaneam|alt="Caperneam" src="HK021E.jpg" size="span" loc="Bottom of page" copy="Horace Knowles" ref="MRK 1:22" \fig*  
\v 23 Ye n…®p…®g a, yermam…ô k…®rik, nanm…®n has ram…ôrer-p…ôn iran. K…®ni in ru…ô m…®n ye nofug…®nien kap…ôri…ô. K…®ni mok-rapomh k…®n Yesu m…®m…ô,  
\v 24 ‚Äú!Eh! !Yesu, yem…ô Nasaret! ?Nakamu…ô ik…®n e m…ô takhawor …ômaw…ô? Tukm…ô ror Ik n…®mau…ô m…ô takoriah …ômaw…ô.‚Äù K…®ni mamni m…®n m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYo yakw…®rkun-ta m…ô Ik e Ik Yem…ô Im…ôrhak…ô kape Kughen.‚Äù\x - \xo 1:24 \xt Mak 5:7 \x*   
\p
\v 25 M…ôr…®g Yesu r…®mn…ôgkiar skai p…ôn k…®mi nanm…®n has ai, m…®m…ô, ‚Äú!Eh! Pim. ∆éta ye yermam…ô e.‚Äù  
\v 26 M…ôknek…®n, nanm…®n has ai ror n…®prai yermam…ô r…ôt…ômn…®m…®n p…®k k…®ni mokr…ôn ehu…ô, m…ôta iran, m…®v…ôn isok.\x - \xo 1:26 \xt Mak 9:26 \x*  
\v 27 K…®ni narmam…ô m…®n…ô aik…®n k…®s…ôm k…®sakur, m…®saiyoh …ôri…ô m…®n…ô mham…ô, ‚Äú!Eh! ?Rhawor e? N…ôgkiarien vi k…®rik e. Kw…ôn e kafan n…ôgkiarien, nanm…®n aik…®n. Tukm…ô In r…ôgkiar k…®mi nanm…®n has m…®n…ô kasor n…ôkwan.‚Äù  
\v 28 M…ôkneik…®n, n…ôvsaoyen kape Yesu r…®t…ôrhav markurao ye Galili.\x - \xo 1:28 \xt Mat 4:24 \x*   
\s1 Yesu r…®mnor huv…ô narmam…ô khapsaah  
\r (Mat 8:14-17; Luk 4:38-41)  
\p
\v 29 M…ôknek…®n Yesu m…®ne Jemes, Saemon m…®ne Andru k…®mnhat…ôrhav ye nim…ô kape nofug…®nien kape n…ôm…ô Isrel mhav…ôn atuatuk ye n…ôkwai nim…ô kape Saemon m…®ne Andru,  
\v 30 m…®s…ôm kuhu Saemon ramokie-okie mamap…®r. K…®ni k…®rh…ôvsao-p…ôn k…®n k…®mi Yesu.  
\v 31 Yesu r…®v…ôn, m…®v…ôh kwerm…®n, m…®vi hakt…ô, k…®ni rhek…®mter. K…®ni ai nokie-okieyen a ror infamien. K…®ni piahwaru ai r…®v…ôn, m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn n…ôv…®g…®nien k…®mi …ôri…ô.   
\p
\v 32 K…®ni r…®namenaiyu, narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®mnhamh…ô, m…®ne narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne nanm…®n has ram…ôm…®r ir…ôri…ô, iri…ô m…®n…ô t…®ks…®n k…®mnhak…®r-p…ô …ôri…ô tuk Yesu.  
\v 33 Narmam…ô m…®n…ô fam a yerkwanu aik…®n, kasofug…®n …ôri…ô m…®n…ô ye kw…ôru…ô ye nim…ô Yesu ramar…ô ik…®n.  
\v 34 K…®ni Yesu ror huv…ô narmam…ô khapsaah yam…ô m…®ne k…®mnhav…ôh n…ômh…ôyen p…®s…®n p…®s…®n. In mam…ôko ta m…®n nanm…®n hah m…®n…ô ye narmam…ô, mamni-…ôhu nanm…®n has m…®n…ô m…ô tukhap…ôh n…®s…ôgkiarien, meinai iri…ô kw…ônharkun-ta In.\x - \xo 1:34 \xt Mak 3:10-12 \x*   
\s1 Yesu ramni…ôrhav kafan n…ôgkiarien apa Galili  
\r (Luk 4:42-44)  
\p
\v 35 K…ôni r…®kwamer k…®n, yenp…®g-enp…®g …ôgk…ôp, Yesu rarar m…®v…ôn apa ik…®n narmam…ô khark…ôk ik…®n mam…ôhuak.\x - \xo 1:35 \xt Mat 14:23; Mak 6:46 \x*  
\v 36 K…®ni ai, Saemon m…®ne in m…®n…ô t…®ks…®n khav…ôn masarha-k…®n In.  
\v 37 K…®s…ôm In, khani-p…ôn tukun mham…ô, ‚ÄúNarmam…ô fam kasarha-k…®n Ik.‚Äù  
\v 38 M…ôr…®g Yesu r…®m…ô, ‚ÄúN…®kam. P…ôh khav…ôn apa yerkwanu p…®s…®n p…®s…®n, ipak…ô tuk …ôtaw…ô. P…ôh yakni-…ôrhav n…ôgkiarien aik…®n, meinai Yo y…®mau…ô tukun.‚Äù  
\v 39 K…®ni ai In r…ôriw…ôk markurao ye Galili, mamni-…ôrhav N…ôgkiarien Huv…ô kape Kughen ye nim…ô kape nofug…®nien kape n…ôm…ô Isrel. Mam…ôkota nanm…®n hah m…®n…ô ye narmam…ô.\x - \xo 1:39 \xt Mat 4:23; 9:35 \x*   
\s1 Yesu r…®mnor huv…ô yermam…ô k…®rik r…®m…®v…ôh n…®mh…ôyen …ôut…ôn k…®rik ye t…®kin  
\r (Mat 8:1-4; Luk 5:12-16)  
\p
\v 40 K…®ni yermam…ô k…®rik yame r…®m…®v…ôh n…®mh…ôyen …ôut…ôn ye t…®kin, in r…®mau…ô m…ôm Yesu, k…®ni m…ôn…®mkur ye n…®mr…®n mamas…ôk. Mamaiyoh k…®n nasituyen, m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTukm…ô nakorkeikei, nak…®rkun nor-huv…ôyen yo.‚Äù  
\v 41 K…®ni Yesu, r…®kin rewaiyu tukun. M…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn kwerm…®n iran, k…®ni m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYakorkeikei m…ô takhuv…ô m…®n. !∆ésan…®n!‚Äù  
\v 42 M…ôknek…®n n…®prai yermam…ô ai rhuv…ô m…®n, n…ômh…ôyen ai r…®rk…ôk m…®n iran.  
\v 43-44 K…®ni Yesu r…ôgkiar skai p…ôn k…®min, m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTakp…ôh n…ôvsaoyen k…®n k…®mi narmam…ô. M…ôr…®g takv…ôn m…ôrer ye n…®mr…® pris, p…ôh in r…ôm m…®n ik. K…®ni ik m…®v…ôn, m…ôhuak m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn nar…®mnar k…®mi Kughen r…ômhen k…®n yame Moses r…®m…®ni m…ô takor, p…ôh narmam…ô k…®s…ôm m…ô nakn…ôsan…®n.‚Äù\x - \xo 1:43-44 \xt Lev 14:1-32 \x*  
\v 45 M…ôr…®g yermam…ô ai r…®m…®t…ôrhav m…ôvsao k…®n k…®mi narmam…ô. Ror p…ôn, Yesu r…®m…ô to r…®p…ôh m…®n n…®v…ônien yerkwanu m…®n…ô m…ôriw…ôk ye n…®mr…® narmam…ô, meinai iri…ô kamhaku-p…ôn p…®k In. K…®ni m…ôr…®g In ram…ôm…®r …ôm…ô apa ik…®n ruhiko ik…®n. Narmam…ô fam khav…ôn mas…ôm In aik…®n.   
\c 2  
\s1 Yesu r…®mnor huv…ô yermam…ô k…®rik yame n…®pran r…®mamh…ô  
\r (Mat 9:1-8; Luk 5:17-26)  
\p
\v 1 N…®p…®g t…®ks…®n ru…ô m…®v…ôn, Yesu r…®rer…®g-p…ôn m…®n yerkwanu e Kapaneam. K…®ni narmam…ô kw…ôs…ôr…®g m…ô In aik…®n.  
\v 2 K…®ni ai, narmam…ô khapsaah khav…ôn aik…®n, mhav…ôn im…ô, kw…ônmhaan r…®m…ôrk…ôsk…ôh. Nim…ô rukwar meriaji kw…ôru…ô r…®sis…ôg. K…®ni ai Yesu ramni-…ôhrav-p…ôn N…ôgkiarien kape Kughen tuk …ôri…ô.  
\v 3 M…ôr…®g n…®p…®g ram…ôgkiar han…ô, narmam…ô kuas khar…ôh yermam…ô k…®rik. N…®pran r…®mamh…ô.  
\v 4 Nim…ô rukwar k…®n narmam…ô, ror p…ôn, iri…ô to khap…ôh nhar…ôhyen yermam…ô ai mhav…ôn ipak…ô tuk Yesu. M…ôr…®g khav…ôn m…®shakt…ô apa tokrei nim…ô, m…®s…ôhipu ta n…®kar nim…ô k…®rik, k…®ni mhar…ôh n…®kaokao yermam…ô ramap…®r-p…ôn iran, mhavi, reiwaiyu-p…ôn.  
\v 5 Yesu r…ôm nhat…ôt…ôyen kap…ôri…ô, m…®ni-p…ôn tuk yermam…ô ai n…®pran r…®mamh…ô, m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúKafak kwajikov…ô. Yo yakw…ôr…ôhsi-ta ta narp…®nien kape t…ôvhag…ô has kafam.‚Äù   
\p
\v 6 M…ôr…®g namhajoun t…®ks…®n kape Loa kape Moses kas…ôkw…ôt…ô, m…®s…ôm norien a, m…®n…ôsaiyoh …ôri…ô m…®n…ô tukun,  
\v 7 mham…ô, ‚Äú!Ah. !Kw…ôn e ramni hah Kughen! N…ôgkiarien e rahas. Kughen p…®s…®n …ôm…ô In r…®rkun n…®r…ôhsitayen narp…®nien kape t…ôvhag…ô hah kape narmam…ô. ?Pa m…®n to r…®rkun n…®v…ôhsi-tayen?‚Äù   
\p
\v 8 M…ôr…®g Yesu ru…®rkun-ta n…ôr…®gien kap…ôri…ô. K…®ni m…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô, m…®m…ô, ‚Äú?Rhawor e nakas…ôr…®g m…ôknek…®n?  
\v 9 ?Jakni-p…ôn naha tuk yermam…ô a, k…®ni k…®mi…ô nakas…ôm …ôfrak…®s? ?M…ô jakni-p…ôn tuk yermam…ô a m…ô kafan t…ôvhag…ô hah yakw…ôr…®s…®n ta? ?U…ô m…ô jakni m…ô in tukrhek…®mter m…®r…ôh kafan n…®kaokao m…ôriw…ôk mamv…ôn?  
