\v 16 Ye n…®p…®g a, n…ômhajoun m…®n…ô t…®ks…®n kape Loa kape Moses k…®m…®s…ôm Yesu. Iri…ô t…®ks…®n a Farisi m…®n…ô, kas…ôm Yesu ram…ôv…®g…®n iri…ô yor t…ôvhag…ô has m…®n…ô, k…®ni k…®n…®saiyoh-p…ôn narmam…ô kape Yesu mham…ô, ‚Äú?Rhawor e kw…ôn e ram…ôv…®g…®n iri…ô yor t…ôvhag…ô has m…®n…ô e?‚Äù\x - \xo 2:16 \xt Mat 11:19 \x*  
