\v 24 K…®ni Farisi m…®n…ô khani-p…ôn tukun mham…ô, ‚Äú!Eh! Sabat e towei, m…ôr…®g iri…ô kasor wok masakap…®r Loa kape Moses. ?Rhawor kafam narmam…ô kasor m…ôknak…®n?‚Äù\f + \fr 2:24 \ft  Loa e kape Moses yame ramni-…ôhu m…ô takp…ôh n…ôsimien ye Sabat. Eks 20:8-11.\f*   
