\v 26 N…®p…®g e in a, Abiata in hae pris kape Kughen. K…®ni m…ôr…®g, Deved r…®mav…ôn ye Nim…ô Ehu…ô kape Kughen mam…ôn bred yame pris m…®n…ô kw…ônhav…ôhsi-p…ôn ta k…®mi Kughen. K…®ni m…ôr…®g Deved r…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn m…®n k…®mi kafan narmam…ô, k…®ni k…®s…ôn. K…®ni m…ôr…®g bred ai, ye Loa kape Moses ramni m…ô narmam…ô apnap…®g tukhap…ôh n…®s…ônien. M…ôr…®g pris m…®n…ô …ôm…ô kharkun n…®s…ônien.‚Äù\f + \fr 2:26 \ft  Kwanage e kape Deved ram…ôm…®r ye 1 Saml 21:1-6\f*   
