\v 18 m…®ne Andru; m…®ne Filip; m…®ne Batalomiu; m…®ne Matiu; m…®ne Tomas; m…®ne Jemes, kwajikov…ô kape Alfeas; m…®ne Tadeas; m…®ne Saemon Selot\f + \fr 3:18 \ft  ‚ÄúSelot‚Äù r…ômhen k…®n yermam…ô k…®rik yame r…®kwas…®g k…®n nukwao kape n…ôm…ô Isrel tuk nherye-rhavyen k…®n gavman kape n…ôm…ô Rom.\f*  
