\v 17 m…ôr…®g khap…ôh nhav…ôhs-huv…ôyen n…ôgkiarien yerkiri…ô, mas…ôrer kape n…®p…®g kwakw…ô …ôm…ô. K…®ni tukm…ô khar…ôhp…®k…®n n…®p…®g …ôut…ôn, u…ô narmam…ô k…®sor ahas p…ôn k…®mi …ôri…ô tuk N…ôgkiarien Huv…ô kape Kughen, m…ôknek…®n kamham…®r.  
\v 18 K…®ni narmam…ô t…®ks…®n yame k…®s…ôr…®g n…ôgkiarien k…®s…ômhen k…®n kweru nai yame r…®mn…ôsaah-p…ôn yerki kw…ônurk…ôs…®k. K…®s…ôr…®g n…ôgkiarien e,  
\v 19 m…ôr…®g kas…ôt…ôr…®g p…®k tuk nar…®mnar kape n…®mraghien kap…ôri…ô. K…®ni naut…ô reiku…ô ir…ôri…ô, m…®vi …ôri…ô, ror r…®kiri…ô ramv…ôn …ôm…ô tuk mane. Norien a roriah n…ôgkiarien kape Kughen, r…®p…ôh norien kw…ônkwan.\x - \xo 4:19 \xt Mat 19:23-24 \x*  
\v 20 K…®ni narmam…ô t…®ks…®n k…®s…ômhen k…®n kweru nai yame r…®mn…ôsaah-p…ôn ye n…®moptan…ô huv…ô. K…®s…ôr…®g n…ôgkiarien a, mharkun. K…®ni mhav…ôh kw…ônkwai n…ôgkiarien a ye nar…ôyen kap…ôri…ô. Iri…ô t…®ks…®n kamhav…ôh kw…ônkwan r…ômhen k…®n toti; t…®ks…®n kamhav…ôh sikisti; k…®ni t…®ks…®n kamhav…ôh kw…ônkwan wan handred ye nar…ôyen kap…ôri…ô.‚Äù   
