\p
\v 21 K…®ni …ôm…ô ai, Yesu r…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTo k…®p…ôh n…®v…ôhyen laet k…®rik kukrai-p…ôn ye n…ôkwai baket, u…ô ye n…ôpag bed. N…®kam. Tukam…ôkeikei k…®ruk hakt…ô.\x - \xo 4:21 \xt Mat 5:15; Luk 11:33 \x*  
\v 22 Tukm…ô nar erkwaig, tukam…ôkeikei k…ôm. Tukm…ô kuvr…®g …ôp…®s, k…®ni m…ôr…®g tukram…ôkeikei mier-p…ô ik…®n rhakak ik…®n.\x - \xo 4:22 \xt Mat 10:26; Luk 12:2 \x*  
