\v 34 In ram…ôgkiar k…®mi narmam…ô apnap…®g ye nuhp…®k…®nien …ôm…ô. M…ôr…®g tukm…ô In m…®ne kafan narmam…ô m…®n…ô, ramhoprai-p…ôn n…®prai n…ôgkiarien kafan k…®mi …ôri…ô.   
