\p K…®ni nanm…®n has ai rokr-apomh m…®m…ô, ‚Äú!Eh! Yesu, Ji Kughen yame In yerp…®r…®g p…®k. ?Nakm…ô takhawor yo e? Yakamaiyoh ik ye nhag Kughen m…ô takp…ôh norien n…ômh…ôyen k…®mi yo.‚Äù\x - \xo 5:7-8 \xt Mak 1:24 \x*   
