\v 11 K…®ni ik…®n a, puk…ôh m…®n…ô khapsaah ik…®n. Kas…ôruk ye n…®hu tukwas a.  
\v 12 K…®ni nanm…®n has m…®n…ô ai k…®sas…ôk mhani-p…ôn tuk Yesu mham…ô, ‚ÄúTak…ôta-p…ôn ir…ômaw…ô yerki puk…ôh m…®n…ô e.‚Äù  
\v 13 K…®ni Yesu reighan k…®n …ôri…ô kamhav…ôn. K…®s…ôta ye yermam…ô ai, k…®ni mhav…ôn yerki puk…ôh m…®n…ô. Puk…ôh m…®n…ô ai khapsaah ipak…ô tuk tu taosen. K…®saiyu m…®seiwaiyu ye n…ôpatu, mhavi-…ôrhav m…®s…ômn…®m ye tahik.   
\p
\v 14 Narmam…ô kape n…ôv…®g…®nien puk…ôh m…®n…ô kas…ôrer aik…®n mas…ôm puk…ôh m…®n…ô kas…ômn…®m, k…®ni k…®saiyu mhav…ôn apa im…ôri…ô ik…®n m…®n…ô, k…®ni m…®s…ôvsao k…®n. K…®ni m…®s…ôvsao apnap…®g k…®n yerkwanu m…®n…ô ipak…ô tuk …ôri…ô. K…®ni narmam…ô ai khav…ôn tukun m…®s…ôm.  
\v 15 Khau…ô m…®s…ôm Yesu, m…®s…ôm yermam…ô ai, nukwao ehu…ô kape nanm…®n has r…®mnam…ôm…®r iran kup…ôn. M…®s…ôm ramkw…ôt…ô m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn neip…ôn. K…®ni n…®rkunien kafan ruahuv…ô. Narmam…ô m…®n…ô ai k…®s…ôm khag…®n.  
\v 16 K…®ni n…ôm…ô m…®n…ô k…®m…®s…ôm Yesu r…®mn…ôkota nanm…®n has k…®s…ôvsao k…®n yermam…ô yame nanm…®n has r…®mnam…ôm…®r iran kupan, m…®ne puk…ôh.  
\v 17 K…®ni n…ôm…ô aik…®n k…®saiyoh-p…ôn skai Yesu m…ô tukr…®t…ôrhav a im…ôri…ô ik…®n.   
\p
\v 18 K…®ni ai Yesu ratp…ôn ye bot. Yermam…ô yame nanm…®n has r…®mnam…ôm…®r iran ramaiyoh-p…ôn In m…ô iriu min.  
\v 19 M…ôr…®g Yesu r…®m…ôni-…ôhu, m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúN…®kam. Takv…ôn apa imam yerkwanu k…®mi…ô kafam narmam…ô m…®n…ô, k…®ni m…ôvsao k…®n nar…®mnar yame Kughen r…®mnor k…®mik, meinai r…®kin r…®mneiwaiyu p…®k tuk ik.‚Äù   
\p
\v 20 K…®ni kw…ôn ai r…®t…ôrhav m…®v…ôn kw…ônmhan k…®rik nhag…®n e Dikapolis, k…®ni mam…ôvsao k…®n norien yame Yesu r…®mnor iran. K…®ni narmam…ô fam k…®s…ôr…®g, k…®sakur k…®n.   
\s1 Yesu r…®mnor huv…ô piraov…®n k…®rik yame r…®m…®v…ôh n…ômh…ôyen, mor huv…ô m…®n piak…ôsk…ôh k…®rik yame r…®mamh…ô ramragh m…®n  
\r (Mat 9:18-26; Luk 8:40-56)  
\p
