\v 56 Ik…®n m…®n…ô fam Yesu ramv…ôn ik…®n, yerkwanu ehu…ô, m…®ne yerkwanu kw…ôskw…ôh, narmam…ô m…®n…ô khap…®k narmam…ô m…®n…ô kamhamh…ô, mas…ôrer …ôswas…®g k…®n ye swatuk p…®si…ôk. K…®ni m…®sas…ôk …ôtg…®n m…ô tukreighaan k…®n narmam…ô kamhamh…ô p…ôh kharap …ôm…ô n…®peihage neip…ôn kafan. K…®ni narmam…ô m…®-fam yam…ô m…®ne k…®mnharap, k…®m…®s…ôsan…®n.   
\c 7  
\s1 N…ômhajoun kape loa kape Moses kamhani hah Yesu  
