\p
\v 1 Namhajoun t…®ks…®n kape loa kape Moses iri…ô Farisi m…®n…ô khas…®-p…ôn Jerusalem mhau…ô m…®sofug…®n-p…ôn tuk Yesu  
\v 2 k…®ni m…®s…ôm m…ô narmam…ô t…®ks…®n kape Yesu kas…ôv…®g…®n mamhav…ôh n…ômk…®m…®k k…®rik meinai khap…ôh n…®s…ôravyen r…ôri-p…ôn natuak…ômien kape n…ôm…ô Isrel.  
\v 3 (Farisi m…®n…ô, m…®ne n…ôm…ô Isrel m…®n…ô fam kamhakwas…®g k…®n nar…ôyen kup…ôn kap…ôri…ô. Tukm…ô khap…ôh n…®s…ôravyen r…ôri-p…ôn norien kap…ôri…ô, to khap…ôh n…®s…ôv…®g…®nien.  
\v 4 K…®ni, tukm…ô khas…®-p…ôn apa maket, mhau…ô yerkwanu, k…®ni mhap…ôh n…®s…ôravyen, to khap…ôh m…®n n…®s…ôv…®g…®nien. Kap…ôri…ô natuak…ômien r…®psaah ye n…®kar…®n kape n…ôspir-tayen n…ômk…®m…®k ye p…ônk…®n, m…®ne sospen m…®ne besin kap…ôri…ô).\f + \fr 7:4 \ft  N…ôm…ô Isrel k…®s…ôuji-p…ôn m…®n loa t…®ks…®n tuk loa kape Moses. K…®ni ai mharai-p…ôn ye n…ôkw…ôkw…ô k…®rik k…®m…ô, Mishnah.\f*   
\p
\v 5 K…®ni Farisi m…®n…ô m…®ne namhajoun kape loa kape Moses k…®n…ôsaiyoh Yesu mham…ô, ‚Äú?Rhawor kafam narmam…ô khap…ôh n…®s…ôri-p…ônien kap…ôtaw…ô natuak…ômien yame kaha m…®n…ô k…®mn…ôs…ôvhag-p…ô k…®n k…®mi …ôtaw…ô? Kafam narmam…ô m…®n…ô kas…ôv…®g…®n mhap…ôh n…®s…ôravyen r…ôri-p…ôn natuak…ômien kap…ôtaw…ô.‚Äù   
\p
\v 6 K…®ni Yesu r…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúEh. Kap…ômi…ô n…®niyen rhuv…ô, m…ôr…®g kap…ômi…ô norien in rahas. In apa kup…ôn, profet k…®rik kape Kughen, nhag…®n e Aesea, r…®mn…ôfrak…®s ye n…®kar…®n kap…ômi…ô m…®rai mamni m…ô,  
\q1 ‚Äú‚ÄòN…ôm…ô m…®n…ô a kamhani apnap…®g …ôm…ô n…ôfrak…®sien irak ye nheri…ô,  
\q2 m…ôr…®g r…®kiri…ô ram…ôm…®r isok p…®k tuk Yo.   
\q1
\v 7 Kas…ôhuak m…ôr…®g kas…ôhuak t…ôkun …ôm…ô.  
\q2 K…®ni kap…ôri…ô n…ôvhagien kamhani mham…ô n…ôgkiarien e kape Kughen, m…ôr…®g ror …ôm…ô n…ôr…®gien k…®n kape yermam…ô.‚Äô‚Äù\rq (Aes 29:13)\rq*   
\p
\v 8 K…®ni Yesu r…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…ô, ‚ÄúK…®mi…ô nakw…ôs…ôp…ôh loa yame Kughen r…®m…®v…ôhsi-pre, k…®ni m…®namhakwas…®g …ôm…ô k…®n n…ôr…®gien kape yermam…ô.‚Äù   
\p
\v 9 K…®ni m…®ni-p…ôn m…®n tuk …ôri…ô m…ô, ‚Äú?K…®mi…ô nakham…ô nakharkun p…®k nar? !M…ôr…®g nakw…ôs…ôp…ôh loa kape Kughen m…®namhakwas…®g …ôm…ô k…®n nar…ôyen kape kaha m…®n…ô!  
\v 10 S…ôm-ru, Moses r…®m…®ni kup…ôn m…®m…ô, ‚ÄòTakhasiai n…®s…®nmi…ô m…®ne r…®m…®mi…ô.‚Äô\rq (Eks 20:12; Dut 5:16)\rq* K…®ni m…®m…ô, ‚ÄòYermam…ô yame ramni hah n…®s…®ni u…ô r…®mni tukhopni.‚Äô\rq (Eks 21:17; Lev 20:9)\rq*  
\v 11 M…ôr…®g k…®mi…ô nakhani-…ôhu narmam…ô m…ô tukhap…ôh n…®sasituyen ye mam…ô m…®ne tat…ô kap…ôri…ô, mham…ô tukhani-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô mham…ô, ‚ÄòEh. Yakeinein n…®v…ôhsi-preyen nar k…®rik meinai yakv…ôhsi-p…ôn ta fam k…®mi Kughen, k…®ni to yakp…ôh n…®v…ôhsi-ta-m…®nien m…®v…ôhsi-pre k…®mik.‚Äô  
\v 12 Nakas…ôvhag k…®mi narmam…ô m…ôknek…®n m…®s…ôtap…®g k…®n nasituyen yame narmam…ô tuksor k…®mi n…®s…®nri…ô m…®ne r…®mri…ô.  
\v 13 Ror p…ôn nar…ôyen kap…ômi…ô yame nakas…ôvhag k…®n k…®mi narmam…ô ramor t…ôkun n…ôgkiarien kape Kughen. K…®ni masor nar…®mnar khapsaah ror m…ôknek…®n.‚Äù   
