\v 25 ?Nakas…ôr…®g m…ô narm…®ragh ehu…ô k…®rik, kamni k…®m…ô kamel, to rauru-p…ôn ye kw…ôruwei nidil u…ô? N…®kam, r…ôut…ôn p…®k. R…ômhen …ôm…ô m…®n k…®n yermam…ô yame kafan naut…ô rehu…ô, r…ôut…ôn p…®k tukun tuk n…ôtayen aik…®n a p…ôh Kughen ramarmaru iran.‚Äù   
