\v 30 nar…®mnar a to khap…ôh nhark…ôk-m…®n-ien tukun. Yermam…ô ai, tukr…®v…ôh tain ye tokrei tan…ô e r…ômhen k…®n wan handred, r…ômhen k…®n nim…ô, m…®ne piauni, m…®ne n…®s…®ni, m…®ne kafan kak…ô, m…®ne kafan kwajikov…ô, m…®ne n…ôsimien kafan (m…ôr…®g tukhauh m…®n in). K…®ni ye nar…ôyen vi kafan, tukrar…ô ye n…®mraghien rer…®n.  
\v 31 M…ôr…®g, narmam…ô m…®n…ô e kas…ôkup…ôn tukpihamakwas…®g, k…®ni yam…ô m…®ne kamhakwas…®g tukpihau…ô m…®pis…ôkup…ôn.‚Äù\x - \xo 10:31 \xt Mat 20:16; Luk 13:30 \x*   
