\v 34 p…ôh tuksarh iakei irak, k…®ni m…®s…ôr…®g-…ôvhin …ôp…ôs Yo, m…®s…ôrk…®s-…ôrk…®s Yo, k…®ni m…®shopni Yo. K…®ni m…ôr…®g jakamragh m…®n ye n…®p…®g yame ror k…®sis…ôr k…®n.‚Äù\x - \xo 10:34 \xt Mak 8:31; 9:31 \x*   
