\v 25 Tukm…ô naks…ôhuak, m…ôr…®g tukm…ô yermam…ô k…®rik r…®mnor nar k…®rik r…®p…ôh n…ômhenien k…®mi …ômi…ô, takhap…ôh n…®sarp…®nien tai kafan t…ôvhag…ô. K…®ni Kughen, R…®m…®mi…ô ye Neai, In tukr…®p…ôh m…®n narp…®nien tai t…ôvhag…ô hah kap…ômi…ô.\x - \xo 11:25 \xt Mat 6:14-15 \x*  
