\p
\v 1 Yermam…ô k…®rik r…®mn…ôsim k…®n grep ye kafan plantesen, markopar…®n-p…ôn. K…®ni m…®k…®r kw…ôt…ôgtap k…®rik kape n…ôvi…ôs…®s-p…ônien kw…ônkwai grep ik…®n. M…ô nehen tukraiyu, k…®v…ôh kor waen k…®n. K…®ni in mor nim…ô apomh k…®rik m…ô tukram…ôrer aik…®n mamarha huv…ô tuk kafan plantesen. K…®ni in m…ôr…ôhu plantesen ai ye kwerm…® narmam…ô t…®ks…®n, tukhap…®k n…ôri…ô t…®ks…®n, mhav…ôh-si-p…ôn nan k…®rik r…ômhen k…®n n…ôrokien. Mar…ô, m…®t…ôrhav m…®n aik…®n m…®v…ôn ye tan…ô p…®s…®n.\x - \xo 12:1 \xt Aes 5:1-2\x*  
\v 2 K…®ni kw…ônkwai grep r…®mhiak, k…®ni yemehu…ô kape plantesen rher-p…ôn k…®n kafan manaja m…ô tukr…®v…ôn m…ôm narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®s…ôsim aik…®n m…ô tukhav…ôhsi-p…ôn grep ne yamehu…ô kape plantesen, r…ômhen k…®n n…ôrok kafan.  
\v 3 M…ôr…®g iri…ô k…®sarar, mharapt…ôr…ôk…®n manaja ai, m…®s…ôrk…®s-…ôrk…®s, m…®sher-p…ôn k…®n m…ô tukr…®rer…®g, mhap…ôh nhav…ôhsi-p…ônien nar k…®rik k…®min.  
