\v 8 M…ôknek…®n kharapt…ôr…ôk…®n, m…®shopni, mhar…ôh n…®pran m…®sarkw…ôrhav k…®n ye n…ôkwai plantesen.‚Äù\f + \fr 12:8 \ft  Yesu ramni nuhp…®k…®nien kape plantesen m…ô n…ôm…ô Isrel k…®m…®shopni profet tu m…®n…ô t…®ks…®n kape Kughen, k…®ni m…ôr…®g ru…®rkun ta m…ô tukshopni m…®n In.\f* \x - \xo 12:8 \xt Hib 13:12 \x*   
\p
\v 9 Yesu r…®ni-p…ôn tuk n…ômehu…ô m…®n…ô ai m…ô, ‚Äú?Yamehu…ô kape plantesen ehu…ô tukrhawor m…®n? Tukr…®v…ôn mhopni-hopni narmam…ô m…®n…ô a, m…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn plantesen ye kwerm…® narmam…ô p…®s…®n.  
