\v 17 K…®ni khar…ôh kot k…®rik r…ôwhao, r…ômhen k…®n kot kape yermaru, m…®sarkaoh-p…ôn k…®n k…®min. K…®ni mhar…ôh n…ôr…ôus k…®rik ror nhir…®n, m…®sor k…ôv…ôvhao k…®n, r…ômhen k…®n k…ôv…ôvhao kape yermaru, mhaukrai-p…ôn ye kap…ôn kap…ô.  
\v 18 K…®ni masokr…ôn k…®n mamhani mham…ô, ‚ÄúIk e yermaru kape n…ôm…ô Isrel. !K…®maw…ô yakamhasiai Ik!‚Äù  
\v 19 K…®ni mamhauh kap…ôn kap…ô k…®n nai, mas…ôr…®g-…ôwhin, k…®ni m…®s…ôn…®mkur ye n…®mr…®n mham…ô kamhasiai In.  
\v 20 K…®ni m…®sarh iakei fam iran, mhar…ôhsi-ta m…®n kot …ôwhao mhav…ôhsi-p…ôn kafan neip…ôn. Mhak…®r mhat…ôrhav, mhav…ôn m…ô tukharuk hakt…ô In ye nai kamarkwao k…®n.   
\s1 Mobael m…®n…ô k…®mnharuk hakt…ô Yesu ye nai kamarkwao k…®n  
\r (Mat 27:32-44; Luk 23:26-43; Jon 19:17-27)  
\p
\v 21 Kamhau…ô ye swatuk, m…®s…ôm yem…ô Saerin k…®rik, nhag…®n e Saemon. In r…®m Aleksanda m…®ne Rufas. In ramv…ôn apa Jerusalem, k…®ni khani-…ôhu m…®sarkut k…®min m…ô tukr…®r…ôh nai kamarkwao k…®n kape Yesu.\x - \xo 15:21 \xt Rom 16:13 \x*  
\v 22 K…®ni iri…ô mhak…®r Yesu mhav…ôn ik…®n k…®rik nhag…®n e Golgota (yame n…®pran r…®m…ô, kw…ônmhaan kape kerh…ô ir…ô jir).\f + \fr 15:22 \ft  N…ôgkiarien e ‚ÄúGolgota‚Äù ye n…ôgkiarien kape n…ôm…ô Rom ramni m…ô ‚ÄúKalfari‚Äù, n…®pran r…®m…ô ‚Äúkerh…ô ir…ô jir.‚Äù\f* \fig K…®m…®s…ôs…®k-p…ôn Yesu ye nai kamarkwao k…®n apa Golgota|alt="Crosses on the outskirts of town" src="HK028B.jpg" size="span" loc="Bottom of page" copy="Horace Knowles" ref="MRK 15:23" \fig*  
\v 23 K…®ni ye kw…ônmhaan a khav…ôhsi-p…ôn waen k…®mi Yesu yame k…ôv…®t-p…ôn n…®mar nai k…®rik kamni k…®m…ô ‚Äúmir‚Äù.\f + \fr 15:23 \ft Tukm…ô ror kam…ôv…®t-p…ôn mir ye waen tuk n…®ni-…ôhuyen n…ôm…ômh…ôyen.\f* M…ôr…®g Yesu r…®p…ôh n…®n…®mien.   
\p
\v 24-25 Ramp…®gp…®g han…ô, k…®mnharuk hakt…ô In ye nai kamarkwao k…®n. K…®ni m…®s…ôwhai kafan neip…ôn masaruk…®n daes tukun, m…ô tukm…ô yame rapita, k…®ni in rav…ôh kafan.\x - \xo 15:24-25 \xt Sam 22:18 \x*  
\v 26 K…®ni k…®rai-p…ôn n…ôgkiarien k…®rik ye nai k…®rik ramni m…ô k…®m…®s…ôm-p…ôn nar has k…®rik iran m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúIn e Yermaru kape n…ôm…ô Isrel.‚Äù K…®ni m…®sarkw…ôt…ôr…ôk…®n-p…ôn ye nai kamarkwao k…®n.  
\v 27 K…®ni mhar…ôh yem…ôkr…ôh mir k…®raru, mharuk hakt…ô m…®n …ôriu iris…®r Yesu. K…®rik ye matuk, k…®rik ye mawor.  
\v 28 M…ôknek…®n, n…ôgkiarien ye N…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen ruau…ô, yame r…®m…ô, ‚ÄúK…®m…ôs…ôvheik…®n In iri…ô n…ôm…ô has m…®n…ô.‚Äù\f + \fr 15:28 \ft  N…ôgkiarien ye v. 28 r…®k…ôk ye kopi akwas t…®ks…®n kape Niutesteman. Keinein m…ô Mak r…®m…®rai …ôfrak…®s u…ô n…®kam.\f*   
\p
\v 29 K…®ni narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôriw…ôk ye swatuk kasarh iakei p…ôn iran. Mas…ôwhan-…ôwhan kap…ôria kap…ô. K…®ni mamhani mham…ô, ‚Äú!In en! !Ik yermam…ô kape natm…ôt…ôg-…ôt…ôgien nim…ô ehu…ô kape Kughen m…®ne nor-m…®nien ye n…®p…®g k…®sis…ôr …ôm…ô!\x - \xo 15:29 \xt Sam 22:7; 109:25; Mak 14:58 \x*  
\v 30 ∆óntah. ∆éta-ru ye nai kamarkwao k…®n meiwaiyu, m…®v…ôh m…®ragh atuk ik.‚Äù   
\p
\v 31 K…®ni jif pris m…®n…ô m…®ne n…ômhajoun m…®n…ô kasarh m…®n iran. Mamhani-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…®n…ô mham…ô, ‚ÄúIn r…®v…ôh m…®ragh ta narmam…ô khapsaah. M…ôr…®g r…®p…ôh n…ômhenien tuk n…®v…ôh-m…®raghien In.  
\v 32 Rhuv…ô m…ô Kristo e, In yermaru kape n…ôm…ô Isrel, tukreiwaiyu ye nai kamarkwao k…®n p…ôh k…®s…ôm, k…®ni mhani n…ôfrak…®sien iran.‚Äù K…®ni kw…ôr…ô mir yame k…®m…®ruk hakt…ô …ôris…®r Yesu kwarpakw…ô k…®mi Yesu.   
\s1 Yesu r…®mamh…ô  
\r (Mat 27:45-56; Luk 23:44-49; Jon 19:28-30)  
\p
\v 33 Yerkweiha …ôm…ô, m…ôr…®g n…ôp…®gn…ôpien ru…ô muvr…®g …ôp…®s tan…®mtan…ô meriaji tri klok.  
\v 34 K…®ni ye tri klok, Yesu rokr…ôn ehu…ô m…®m…ô, ‚Äú!Elae! !Elae! ?Lama sabaktani?‚Äù N…®pran r…®m…ô, ‚Äú!Kughen kafak! !Kughen kafak! ?Rhawor nakamapitan k…®n Yo?‚Äù\f + \fr 15:34 \ft  Yesu ram…ôni Ol Sam 22:1 ik…®n e. N…®mh…ôyen kape Yesu r…®mnor fulfilem ye profesi ye Ol Sam 22.\f*   
\p
\v 35 K…®ni narmam…ô t…®ks…®n yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôrer aik…®n m…®s…ôr…®g n…ôgkiarien ai mham…ô, ‚ÄúS…ôr…®g-ru. In ramokr…ôn k…®n Elaeja.‚Äù  
\v 36 K…®ni kw…ôn k…®rik raiyu …ôtkin m…®v…ôn m…®r…ôh n…®p…ôrp…ôr neip…ôn meires ye waen …ôkwahir. M…ôrk…®s-p…ôn ye nai apomh k…®rik k…®ni m…®v…ôhsi-hakt…ô p…ôn k…®mi Yesu m…ô tukr…®n…®m. K…®ni m…®m…ô, ‚Äú?P…ôh k…®s…ôm-ru m…ô to Elaeja ru…ô masitu iran u…ô?‚Äù\x - \xo 15:36 \xt Sam 69:21 \x*   
\p
\v 37 M…ôr…®g Yesu rar…ô mokr…ôn ehu…ô m…®n k…®ni ai kafan neihagien r…®t…ôrhav.   
\p
\v 38 Kafan neihagien r…®t…ôrhav aik…®n, k…®ni n…ôkwai nim…ô ehu…ô kape Kughen, k…®m…®ruk hakt…ô neip…ôn k…®rik yame k…®mn…ôtap…®g k…®n Kw…ônmhan yame R…ôm…ôrhak…ô M…ôm…ôrhak…ô p…®k. Neip…ôn a r…ôhipu n…®p…ôr…®n k…®raru. R…ôhipu apa yerp…®r…®g …ôgk…ôp meiwaiyu.  
\v 39 K…®ni yamehu…ô kape mobael yame ram…ôrer ipak…ô tuk Yesu m…ôm n…®mh…ôyen kape Yesu k…®ni m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúN…ôfrak…®sien. Kw…ôn e In Ji Kughen.‚Äù   
\p
\v 40 K…®ni Meri, pian Magdala, m…®ne Salome, m…®ne Meri n…®s…®n kwajikov…ô mir nhagriu Jemes m…®ne Joses, karharer isok, iri…ô n…®piraov…®n t…®ks…®n mas…ôm In.\x - \xo 15:40 \xt Luk 8:2-3 \x*  
\v 41 N…®p…®g Yesu r…®mav…ôn Galili, iris…®r ai karh…®kwas…®g k…®n In, m…®rhasitu iran. K…®ni n…®piraov…®n apnap…®g m…®n…ô khapsaah apaik…®n, k…®mnhat…ôrhav-p…ôn Jerusalem iri…ô min mhau…ô.   
\s1 Josef yem…ô Aramatia r…®m…®n…®m Yesu  
\r (Mat 27:57-61; Luk 23:50-56; Jon 19:38-42)  
\p
\v 42 N…®p…®g a, kamni k…®m…ô napn…ôpen…ôyen meinai t…®k…ôni r…®kwamer k…®n n…®p…®g kape Sabat. Ipak…ô m…®rh riv…ô,  
\v 43 Josef, yem…ô Aramatia k…®rik, r…®t…ôrhav-p…ô. In yermam…ô k…®rik kape kaonsel kap…ôri…ô, yame yermam…ô kamhasiai in. K…®ni in m…®n rawhin narmaruyen kape Kughen m…ô tukru…ô. Ramg…®n pawk, m…ôr…®g r…®mnarar m…®v…ôn m…ôm Paelat, maiyoh in m…ô tukreighaan k…®n n…®prai Yesu.  
\v 44 Paelat r…®mn…ôr…®g m…ô Yesu r…®mamh…ô aihuaa …ôm…ô, rakur p…®k k…®n. K…®ni mokr…ôn k…®n yamehu…ô kape mobael maiyoh in m…®m…ô, ‚Äú?Yesu ruamh…ô …ôfrak…®s u…ô?‚Äù   
\p
\v 45 K…®ni yamehu…ô ai reighan k…®n. K…®ni Paelat reighan k…®n Josef m…ô tukr…®v…ôn m…®r…ôh n…®prai Yesu.  
\v 46 K…®ni Josef r…®v…ôn m…®r…ôhsi-…ôhu n…®pran ye nai kamarkwao k…®n, m…®v…ôn m…®v…ôh n…®mr…® neip…ôn huv…ô k…®rik mu…ô muvr…®g n…®pran k…®n neip…ôn a. K…®ni m…®r…ôh m…®v…ôn m…ôr…ôhu ye n…ôpag kapier k…®rik yame k…®nor huv…ô ta. K…®ni m…ôtap…®g …ôswas…®g k…®n kapier ehu…ô k…®rik.  
\v 47 Ye n…®p…®g a, Meri, pian Magdala, m…®ne Meri n…®s…®n Joses, iriu k…®maw…ôm kw…ônmhaan yame r…®mn…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn Yesu ik…®n.   
\c 16  
\s1 Yesu r…®mamragh m…®n ye n…®mh…ôyen  
\r (Mat 28:1-8; Luk 24:1-12; Jon 20:1-10)  
\p
\v 1 R…®namenaiyu, n…®p…®g kape Sabat r…®namor infamien, Meri, pian Magdala, m…®ne Salome, m…®ne Meri, n…®s…®n Jemes, krh…®v…ôn m…®rh…®v…ôh n…®mr…® n…®mar nai t…®ks…®n yame n…ômiov…®n rapien huv…ô. M…®rh…®v…ôn m…ô tukrhor-p…ôn ye n…®prai Yesu.  
\v 2 K…ôni r…®kwamer k…®n, ye Sande, yenp…®g-enp…®g …ôgk…ôp, krh…®v…ôn ik…®n n…®prai Yesu ram…ôm…®r ik…®n. M…®rh r…®rikakun mamhakt…ô,  
\v 3 karh…®v…ôn han…ô ye swatuk, marh…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôris…®r m…®rh…®m…ô, ‚Äú?Pa tukrasitu ir…ôtas…®r tuk n…ôsoktayen k…®n kapier yame k…®mnhaukrai …ôswas…®g p…ôn tuk Yesu?‚Äù  
\v 4 Iris…®r k…®rh…®ni m…ôknaik…®n meinai kapier a in rehu…ô p…®k, m…ôr…®g karh…®ni han…ô marharha-p…ôn, m…®rh…ôm m…ô k…®n…ôsok ta k…®n kapier a.   
\p
\v 5 Karh…®v…ôn im…ô ye n…ôpag kapier ai, m…®rh…ôm p…®kwarien k…®rik, kafan kot r…ôpomh mhaw…ôn. Ramkw…ôt…ô ye kwerm…®ris…®r matuk. K…®rh…ôm, k…®rhakur.  
\v 6 M…ôr…®g r…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôris…®r m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTakrh…®p…ôh n…®rh…®g…®nien. Yak…®rkun m…ô nakarharhak…®n Yesu yem…ô Nasaret, yame k…®m…®ruk hakt…ô ye nai kamarkwao k…®n. M…ôr…®g In r…®rk…ôk eik…®n e. Ru…®mragh ta. Rhu…ôru m…®rh…ôm. Tamhek…®n e k…®mn…ôr…ôhu ik…®n.  
\v 7 Takrh…®v…ôn m…®rh…®ni-…ôrhav-p…ôn tuk narmam…ô m…®ne Pita m…®rh…®m…ô, ‚ÄòIn r…®n…ôkup…ôn ta k…®n …ômi…ô muav…ôn apa Galili. Nakharkun n…®s…ômien In aik…®n, r…ômhen k…®n yame In ru…®n…®-pre ta tuk …ômi…ô.‚Äô‚Äù\x - \xo 16:7 \xt Mat 26:32; Mak 14:28 \x*  
\v 8 K…®ni pia mis…®r a krh…®t…ôrhav, meinai k…®m…®rh…®g…®n p…®k, k…®ni marh…ôt…ômn…®m…®n. Ror p…ôn krh…®p…ôh n…®rh…®ni-…ôsah-p…ônien tuk narmam…ô.\f + \fr 16:8 \ft  Kopi akwas t…®ks…®n kape Niutesteman ye n…ôgkiarien kape n…ôm…ô Gris kharp…®n n…ôgkiarien ye ves 8 mham…ô, ‚ÄúM…ôr…®g n…®piraov…®n m…®n…ô ai k…®mnhau…ô m…®s…ôvsao-p…ôn k…®n k…®mi Pita m…®ne narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôm…®r aik…®n. M…®s…ôvsao k…®n nar…®mnar yame kw…ôn ai r…®m…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô. Kwas…®g ik…®n ye nar…®mnar m…®n…ô a Yesu atuk r…®ta…ôrhav-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn n…ôgkiarien k…®mi …ôri…ô m…ô tukhat…ôrhav m…®sarkurao ye tan…®mtan…ô m…®s…ôvsao k…®n N…ôgkiarien Huv…ô kape Kughen. N…ôgkiarien ai ramni m…ô Kughen r…®rkun n…®w…ôh-m…®raghien narmam…ô m…®rkun n…ômviviyen narmam…ô kape rer…®n.‚Äù\f*   
\s1 Yesu r…®mamragh m…®n, narmam…ô khapsaah kas…ôm In\f + \fr 16:9 \ft  N…ôgkiarien ye v. 9 meriaji 20, r…®rk…ôk ye kopi akwas t…®ks…®n kape Niutesteman. Keinein m…ô pa nhag…®n r…®m…®rai.\f*  
\r (Mat 28:9-10; Jon 20:11-18)  
\p
\v 9 Yesu rar…ô m…®mragh m…®n ye Sande yenp…®g-enp…®g …ôgk…ôp. Aik…®n m…®t…ôrhav-p…ô tuk Meri, pian Magdala yame Yesu r…®mn…ôkota nanm…®n has seven iran kup…ôn.  
\v 10 K…®ni pian ai r…®v…ôn m…ôm narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®mn…ômhakwas…®g k…®n Yesu, yame kas…ôr…®g rahas p…®k tukun, m…®sas…ôk. M…ôvsao-p…ôn k…®n k…®mi …ôri…ô.  
\v 11 M…ôr…®g n…®p…®g k…®m…®s…ôr…®g m…ô Yesu r…®m…®mragh m…®n k…®ni Meri m…®n r…®mn…ôm, iri…ô khap…ôh nhanien n…ôfrak…®sien iran.   
\p
\v 12 K…®ni ai, yermam…ô mir k…®raru kape Yesu kaweriw…ôk ye swatuk, Yesu r…®t…ôrhav-p…ôn tuk …ôriu. N…®pran rukrek…®n p…®s…®n.  
\v 13 K…®ni k…®rarer…®g m…®rav…ôn mw…ôvsao k…®n k…®mi narmam…ô m…®n…ô kafan; m…ôr…®g khap…ôh nhaniyen n…ôfrak…®sien iran.   
\s1 Yesu r…®mat…ôrhav-p…ô tuk kafan narmam…ô m…®n…ô  
\r (Mat 28:16-20; Luk 24:36-49; Jon 20:19-23; Wok 1:6-8)  
\p
\v 14 Kasar…ô mamhav…ôn, narmam…ô leven kape Yesu kas…ôv…®g…®n, Yesu r…®t…ôrhav-p…ôn m…®n tuk …ôri…ô; k…®ni m…ôgkiar-p…ôn skai k…®mi …ôri…ô meinai iri…ô khap…ôh n…®shat…ôt…ôyen iran. K…®ni kaparhia kap…ô r…®skai p…®k. In r…®mn…ôgkiar skai p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô meinai khap…ôh m…®n nhaniyen n…ôfrak…®sien ye n…ôgkiarien kape narmam…ô m…®n…ô t…®ks…®n yame k…®m…®s…ôm In, mamhani-…ôrhav m…ô r…®m…®mragh m…®n.\x - \xo 16:14 \xt 1 Kor 15:5 \x*  
\v 15 K…®ni r…®ni-p…ôn tuk kafan narmam…ô m…®n…ô m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTaks…ôkeikei mhav…ôn m…®sarkurao ye tan…®mtan…ô mhani-…ôrhav n…ôgkiarien huv…ô kape Kughen.\x - \xo 16:15 \xt Wok 1:8 \x*  
\v 16 Yermam…ô yame rhat…ôt…ô irak, k…®ni mor baptaes, Kughen tukr…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn n…®mraghien rer…®n k…®min. M…ôr…®g yermam…ô yame r…®p…ôh n…®niyen n…ôfrak…®sien irak, Kughen tukr…®ni m…ô tukr…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn narp…®nien k…®min m…ô tukr…®v…ôn apa ye nap ehu…ô.\x - \xo 16:16 \xt Wok 2:38 \x*  
\v 17 K…®ni narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®shat…ôt…ô irak, Kughen tukror n…®mt…ôtien t…®ks…®n ye n…®mraghien kap…ôri…ô. Tukharkun n…®s…ôkotayen nanm…®n has ye narmam…ô ye nhag…®k; mharkun m…®n n…®niyen n…ôgkiarien p…®s…®n p…®s…®n;\x - \xo 16:17 \xt Wok 2:4; 8:7 \x*  
\v 18 mharkun n…®r…ôhyen snek, m…ôr…®g snek to r…®p…ôh n…ôsien …ôri…ô; mharkun n…®n…®mien kakon…ô, m…ôr…®g to khap…ôh nhamh…ôyen k…®n; mharkun n…ôr…ôhu-p…ônien kwerm…®ri…ô ye narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kamamh…ô, k…®ni tuks…ôsan…®n.‚Äù\x - \xo 16:18 \xt Luk 10:19; Wok 28:3-6 \x*   
\p
\v 19 Yesu Yermaru ram…ôgkiar infamien, Kughen r…®v…ôh In mhakt…ô m…®v…ôn ye rao ye neai. Takt…ôkun ai, In ramkw…ôt…ô ye kwerm…® Kughen matuk.\x - \xo 16:19 \xt Wok 1:9-11; 2:33-34 \x*  
\v 20 K…®ni narmam…ô kafan k…®mnhat…ôrhav m…®s…ôvsao k…®n N…ôgkiarien Huv…ô ik…®n m…®n…ô fam. K…®ni In ramasitu ir…ôri…ô. K…®ni mamor n…®mt…ôtien r…®psaah ye n…®mraghien kap…ôri…ô m…ô narmam…ô tukhani n…ôfrak…®sien iran.\x - \xo 16:20 \xt Wok 14:3; Hib 2:3-4 \x*   